@startuml Meetsendai_V0_EndToEnd_Sequence
title Meetsendai V0 - End-to-End Flow (Onboarding to Lead Capture)
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
skinparam BoxPadding 10

legend top right
  **Risk Levels (Transactions & Actor Swimlanes)**
  |<#White> Black Arrow | Internal / Low Risk Operation |
  |<#F2F9FF> Light Blue Box | Trusted Internal System Boundary |
  |<#Orange> Orange Arrow | PII Processing / Auth (Medium Risk) |
  |<#FFE6CC> Light Orange Box| Edge Transit / 3rd Party (Medium Risk) |
  |<#Red> Red Arrow | External PII Ingress-Egress (High Risk) |
  |<#FFCCCC> Light Red Box| Untrusted External Actors (High Risk) |
endlegend

box "Internal Operations" #E6F2FF
actor "Sales / CRM" as CRM
actor "Finance" as Finance
end box

box "Trusted Cloud Hub — EU Only (Low Risk Env)" #F2F9FF
participant "CI/CD Pipeline" as Pipeline
participant "Terraform (IaC)" as TF
participant "Azure Infrastructure\n(EU Region)" as Azure
participant "Azure Key Vault\n(TDE Key Management)" as KV
participant "Azure App (Docker)" as Docker
participant "PostgreSQL DB\n(EU, TLS 1.3 + TDE)" as DB
participant "AI Engine\n(Whisper / OCR)" as AI
end box

box "Auth (Med Risk)" #FFE6CC
participant "Auth0" as IDP
end box

box "External Actors (High Risk)" #FFCCCC
actor "Client Tenant Admin" as Admin
actor "Sales Rep (Event)" as Rep
actor "Lead" as Lead
end box

== 1. Sales & Financial Approval ==
CRM -> Finance: Sale Completed (Request Order Approval)
activate Finance
Finance -> Pipeline: Approves Order & Triggers Provisioning
deactivate Finance

== 2. Automated Infrastructure Provisioning (EU) ==
activate Pipeline
Pipeline -> TF: Execute Terraform Plan/Apply for New Tenant
activate TF
TF -> Azure: Provision PostgreSQL DB\n(Enterprise: dedicated instance; Shared tiers: RLS policy on shared instance)
TF -> KV: Create/Assign Azure Key Vault TDE Key\n(Enterprise: dedicated; Shared tiers: shared key)
Azure --> TF: DB Provisioned & Encrypted (TLS 1.3 + TDE)
TF -[#orange]-> IDP: Configure Tenant Auth (Auth0)
IDP --[#orange]-> TF: Auth configured
TF --> Pipeline: Provisioning Complete
deactivate TF
Pipeline -> CRM: Client Created & Infrastructure Ready
deactivate Pipeline

== 3. Client Tenant Event Setup ==
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: Login via Auth0
Docker -[#orange]-> IDP: Validate Credentials
IDP --[#orange]-> Docker: Auth Token
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: Upload Product Documentation
Docker -> DB: Store Docs in Tenant DB
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: Create New Tracking Event

== 4. Lead Capture Workflow (EU Processing) ==
Rep -[#orange]-> IDP: Login via Auth0
IDP --[#orange]-> Rep: Auth Token
Rep -> Docker: Select Event
note right
  App passes signed location header
  to indicate EU data context.
  No external geo-routing in V0.
end note
Rep -[#red]-> Rep: Scan Business Card (OCR)\n& Record Voice Note
Rep -[#red]-> Docker: Submit Lead Data (Photo + Audio)\nvia HTTPS / TLS 1.3

activate Docker
Docker -[#orange]-> AI: Pass Audio & Image for OCR + Transcription
activate AI
AI --[#orange]-> Docker: Extracted Contact Data & Voice Transcript
deactivate AI
Docker -> DB: Fetch Product Docs for Cross-Reference
DB --> Docker: Product Docs
Docker -[#orange]-> AI: Analyse Transcript vs Product Docs
activate AI
AI --[#orange]-> Docker: Generated Draft Email
deactivate AI
Docker -[#orange]-> DB: Store Lead PII & Draft\n(Encrypted via TDE, RLS enforces tenant_id isolation)
Docker --[#orange]-> Rep: Present Draft Email for Review
deactivate Docker

== 5. Human-in-the-Loop & Delivery ==
Rep -[#orange]-> Docker: Review & Approve Draft
Docker -[#red]-> Lead: Dispatch via Email

== 6. Compliance / Admin ==
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: View Event Metrics (Scoped to Tenant)
Admin -[#red]-> DB: Query/Delete Subject Data (GDPR Request)
@enduml
